===============================================================================
                         AVAILABLE RACES
===============================================================================

AetherMUD features 51 playable races from the Rifts universe:

DRAGONS:
  adult_dragon          - Mature dragon (immense power)
  ancient_dragon        - Ancient dragon (legendary)
  dragon_hatchling      - Young dragon (growing power)
  great_horned_dragon   - Shapeshifter dragon (metamorph ability)
  thorny_dragon         - Armored dragon (natural MDC)

HUMANS & VARIANTS:
  human                 - Standard human (versatile)
  true_atlantean        - Atlantean (magic affinity, tattoos)
  promethean            - Engineered human (enhanced)
  cosmo_knight          - Cosmic champion (divine power)

D-BEES (DIMENSIONAL BEINGS):
  dog_boy               - CS mutant (enhanced senses)
  psi_stalker           - Psionic predator (hunts magic users)
  simvan              - Monster rider (beast master)
  wolfen              - Wolf humanoid (warrior culture)
  noli                  - Peaceful race (healer)
  uteni                 - Aquatic humanoid  
  eandroth              - Mystical being
  trimadore             - Mysterious traveler

DWARVES & ELVES:
  dwarf                 - Sturdy craftsman (tough, skilled)
  elf                   - Graceful immortal (magic affinity)
  gnome                 - Small tinkerer (inventive)
  halfling              - Small wanderer (luck bonus)

GIANTS & LARGE BEINGS:
  ogre                  - Brutal giant (high strength)
  troll                 - Regenerating giant (regeneration)
  titan_juicer          - Enhanced giant (mega-juicer variant)
  minotaur              - Bull-headed warrior (strength + rage)

SUPERNATURAL:
  godling               - Demigod (immense power)
  demon                 - Demonic being (evil powers)
  deevil                - Infernal being (cunning)
  vampire               - Undead predator (blood drinker)
  nightbane             - Shapeshifter (dark mirror form)
  werewolf              - Lycanthrope (beast transformation)

SPLUGORTH MINIONS:
  splugorth             - Master slaver (powerful)
  splugorth_minion      - Servant race
  splynn_slave          - Enslaved being
  brodkil               - Demon mercenary

PSYCHICS:
  burster               - Pyrokinetic (fire powers)
  mind_melter           - Master psychic (powerful psionics)
  mind_bleeder          - Defensive psychic
  psi_ghost             - Invisible psychic
  psi_healer            - Healing psychic

GOBLINS & SMALL RACES:
  goblin                - Sneaky humanoid (quick)
  orc                   - Warrior humanoid (strong)
  hobgoblin             - Larger goblin (military)

JUICER VARIANTS:
  mega_juicer           - Enhanced juicer (extreme power)
  dragon_juicer         - Dragon blood juicer (unique)
  quick_flex            - Lightning juicer (speed)

MONSTERS & UNIQUE:
  gargoyle              - Stone creature (flight, MDC)
  changeling            - Shapeshifter (perfect disguise)
  mutant_animal         - Evolved animal (varies)
  cat_girl              - Feline humanoid

UNUSUAL:
  minion                - Bound servant

===============================================================================
To see details on a specific race: help <race_name>
Example: help human, help dragon, help psi_stalker
===============================================================================
